Circuit:

       ________________________________
vcc --| VCC                        PB4 |---- RED_LED
      |                            PB3 |---- GREEN_LED
      |                            PB2 |---- BLUE_LED
      |                            PB1 |---- BUZZER
      |           ATTINY24A        PA3 |---- MOTOR
      |                            PA2 |---- BUTTON
  |---| GND                        PA1 |---- DOOR
  |   |________________________________|
 _|_
 \ /


